Usage: getDbGetMode [-help] [-displayFormat] [-displayLimit] [-escapeBusChar]
                    [-quiet] [-nonDefault]

-help                           # Prints out the command usage
-displayFormat                  # How to present the objects and attributes on
                                # stdout  (enums={simple table}, default=simple)
-displayLimit                   # Number of objects to be shown with dbGet 
                                # (int, default=10)
-escapeBusChar                  # Whether to escape bus characters
                                # (bool, default=true)
-quiet                          # Displays the current settings in Tcl list format only
-nonDefault                     # Displays the current settings which are not default settings